160
00:08:27,562 --> 00:08:30,544
which kind of led to this education fatigue of like,

161
00:08:30,544 --> 00:08:36,026
what am I doing, where am I going, how long is this, can I stop now type of mentality.

162
00:08:37,649 --> 00:08:41,593
