982
00:55:27,653 --> 00:55:33,980
showing this kind of roadmap pathway of how players can graduate to these other segments.

983
00:55:35,740 --> 00:55:38,624
Create diverse ways to teach players the necessary content.

984
00:55:38,624 --> 00:55:42,469
You can do this through UI visuals, in-world visuals,

985
00:55:42,469 --> 00:55:44,451
gameplay demonstrations, audio feedback,

986
00:55:44,451 --> 00:55:47,134
and you need to find some catch-alls if you can.

