00:55:47,134 --> 00:55:48,816
Because if a player is struggling

988
00:55:48,816 --> 00:55:51,339
and they're still not getting it,

989
00:55:51,339 --> 00:55:53,001
then they're probably just gonna put your game down.

990
00:55:55,602 --> 00:55:58,123
And lastly, pace out the content appropriately.

991
00:55:58,123 --> 00:56:00,844
Reward players along the way.

992
00:56:00,844 --> 00:56:02,585
Create force breaks and spots for players

993
00:56:02,585 --> 00:56:04,046
to see their progress.

